<quantity box="[1192,1251,493,520]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="10" pageNumber="146" unit="cm" value="3.0">3 cm</quantity>
long, acute, cuneate to attenuate at base ............................................................................................................... 3
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[189,1399,493,629]" pageId="10" pageNumber="146">
<keyLead pageId="10" pageNumber="146">
– Opposite leaves on stems dimorphic; lamina ovate, more than 
<quantity box="[999,1059,566,593]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="10" pageNumber="146" unit="cm" value="3.0">3 cm</quantity>
long, cordate to rounded at base ................................................................................................................................................... 4
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="10" pageNumber="146">
<paragraph blockId="10.[189,1414,669,804]" pageId="10" pageNumber="146">
<keyLead pageId="10" pageNumber="146">
